'''Saarai''' was a combination of [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] and [[Sith/Legends|Sith]] teachings developed by [[Nikkos Tyris]]. It combined Tyris's own [[Jedi training/Legends|Jedi training]] with the techniques he learned from the [[Holocron/Legends|holocron]] of [[Volfe Karkko]]. Tyris eventually left the [[Jedi Order/Legends|Jedi Order]] and became one of [[Count/Legends|Count]] [[Dooku/Legends|Dooku's]] [[Dark Acolyte/Legends|Dark Acolytes]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].

In the [[Sith (language)|Sith]], "saarai" meant "truth." The followers of these teachings were called [[Jensaarai/Legends|Jensaarai]], or "hidden followers of truth." Their leader was called the [[Saarai-kaar]], or "keeper of truth."

